Program: Discovery
Title: Matters Of The Heart - part one
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jry6p
Last Broadcast Date: 16 September 2002
How Magnetic Resonance Imaging (MRI) has given doctors a new understanding of the heart. An examination of how we have gained a better understanding of the heart over the last two decades. Presenter: Geoff Watts. Producer: Adrian Washbourne.